{"tid":1614153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家我地輸緊","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:56:43.000Z","uid":73783,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ee8f4b18938884c44993b932307db2c63d5423","tid":1614153,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"諗返當日，一個少女俾人射爆眼<br />\n我地做左d咩<br />\n去圍堵機場<br />\n停佢飛呀<br />\n全日航班停晒<br />\n係贏左勝利一仗<br />\n<br />\n而家呢，黑警殺人呀<br />\n我地今日做咩呀<br />\n繼續返工<br />\n當冇事發生過<br />\n夜晚先出黎<br />\n但效果同平時一樣<br />\n<br />\n你話，警察向市民開實彈槍<br />\nd人竟然唔嬲<br />\n咩都唔做<br />\n我地唔係輸撚緊係咩<br />\n<br />\n仲係停留在商場叫口號<br />\n拉人鍊<br />\n我係政府都睬q你la<br />\n拉晒d勇武<br />\n就剩返d和理非<br />\n連罷工都唔敢既和理非<br />\n政府唔係贏撚緊係咩<br />\n我而家真係好憤怒"},{"pid":"e064dd945fbab3f89b6c937a5dd634feb9459ad4","tid":1614153,"uid":277644,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/392779791327276/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F392779791327276%2F&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7AexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=2fe4493f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/392779791327276/</a><br />\n狗癲撚左啊"},{"pid":"3dcd7351a609b7c230000f17580bb7b1875946a8","tid":1614153,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"【和勇合一，遍地開花戰略】大家要全民升級，就去政府合署度讀臨時議會宣言！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"be6031bcafe4456f643651f3b7a91ae0a4768b1a","tid":1614153,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"其實而家再多核彈都冇用<br />\n市民就係得咁多<br />\n見晒底"},{"pid":"6a26869780a1dedc0fe4961b6d18095848dd8654","tid":1614153,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e064dd945fbab3f89b6c937a5dd634feb9459ad4","tid":1614153,"uid":277644,"like":1,"d